<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أي لا دواء له.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وإذا لقي الشدة بكاملها قالوا:</span> ٣٩٦: <span class="c1">"لقيها بأصبارها"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[وقالوا في العداة]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">٣٩٧:</span> <span class="c1">"هم سود الأكباد"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
